<i>♪ And we will run, we will ♪</i>

1266
01:31:46,418 --> 01:31:48,216
<i>♪ And we will crawl, we will ♪</i>

1267
01:31:48,378 --> 01:31:52,428
<i>♪ I would like to hold my little hand ♪</i>

1268
01:31:52,590 --> 01:31:54,592
<i>♪ And we will run, we will ♪</i>

1269
01:31:54,759 --> 01:31:56,761
<i>NARRATOR:
But the happiest part of the story</i>

1270
01:31:56,928 --> 01:31:59,147
<i>is that Matilda and Miss Honey</i>

1271
01:31:59,305 --> 01:32:02,149
<i>each got what they had
always wanted:</i>

1272
01:32:02,308 --> 01:32:04,982
<i>A loving family.</i>

1273
01:32:06,521 --> 01:32:10,492
<i>And Matilda never had
to use her powers again.</i>

1274
01:32:10,859 --> 01:32:13,783
<i>Well, I mean, almost never.</i>

1275
01:32:14,738 --> 01:32:17,867
<i>♪ On my way, on my way ♪</i>

1276
01:32:18,825 --> 01:32:22,045
<i>♪ On my way, on my way ♪</i>

